OL,6,FThe mother of two murdered sisters
OL,7,Fsaid an apology from the Metropolitan
OL,8,FPolice "felt like a slap in the face",
OL,9,Fafter two officers were jailed for
OL,10,Fsharing photos of their bodies.
OL,12,FMina Smallman told Desert Island Discs
OL,13,Fthat she was "celebrating" when the
OL,14,Fconstables were jailed, adding that
OL,15,F"hidden pockets of filth" had been
OL,16,F"allowed to blossom" in the force.
