OL,3,CMet apology felt like a slap in the
OL,4,Cface, says mother of murdered sisters
OL,6,FMs Smallman's daughters, Nicole
OL,7,FSmallman, 27, and Bibaa Henry, 46,
OL,8,Fwere stabbed to death while
OL,9,Fcelebrating a birthday in a park in
OL,10,FWembley, north-west London, in June
OL,11,F2020.
OL,13,FDanyal Hussein was jailed for a
OL,14,Fminimum of 35 years for murdering them
OL,15,Fas part of a Satanic blood pact.
OL,17,FFormer Met constables Deniz Jaffer and
OL,18,FJamie Lewis were jailed for two years
OL,19,Fand nine months for sharing
OL,20,Fphotographs of the sisters on WhatsApp.
