OL,3,CMet apology felt like a slap in the
OL,4,Cface, says mother of murdered sisters
OL,6,FThey described them as "dead birds" in
OL,7,Fthe messaging groups.
OL,9,FFormer Met Commissioner Dame Cressida
OL,10,FDick issued a public apology in 2021
OL,11,Fon behalf of the force to the family.
OL,13,FAsked what her response to that
OL,14,Fapology was, Ms Smallman told the BBC
OL,15,FRadio 4 programme: "It felt like a
OL,16,Fslap in the face, really. You say
OL,17,Fsorry when you bump into someone at
OL,18,Fthe supermarket.
OL,20,F"Another issue with huge institutions
OL,21,Fis the arrogance."
